betterquesting:10.desc:8:
As I am becoming more well-versed in thaumaturgy, things are starting to make more sense...
Well, they make less sense, but I can 'feel' more...
And I now feel like crabs are part of something bigger...
They are not from this world, well, not originally, they come from somewhere else, many generations ago, and they eventually evolved here on Terra to adapt to the current environment.
The crimson cult, the unfriendly order of thaumaturgists that I have encountered, are also not natives of Terra. Indeed, they are capable of opening wormholes.
